  "title": "chore(deps): update dependency jsdom-global to v3",
  "body": "<p>This Pull Request updates dependency <a href=\"https://github.com/rstacruz/jsdom-global\">jsdom-global</a> from <code>v2.1.1</code> to <code>v3.0.2</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"commits\">Commits</h3>\n<p><details><br />\n<summary>rstacruz/jsdom-global</summary></p>\n<h4 id=\"302\">3.0.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rstacruz/jsdom-global/commit/58ca23634a566de48185ae8d5d20ff099ccd9496\"><code>58ca236</code></a> Mark jsdom as a peerDependency</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rstacruz/jsdom-global/commit/cc7284a8b54d6960e5f42152e84f990b1e3f0503\"><code>cc7284a</code></a> Release v3.0.1</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"301\">3.0.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rstacruz/jsdom-global/commit/bb015bfd4b5d5681ef4c0bd901e47751f5e863f5\"><code>bb015bf</code></a> Merge pull request #&#8203;17 from Cinematique/master</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rstacruz/jsdom-global/commit/297b2c1e5a03741365855660c26fef68f082d42d\"><code>297b2c1</code></a> Release v3.0.0</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"300\">3.0.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rstacruz/jsdom-global/commit/3050b2edae9ff68a68c343d8d411a7892324f513\"><code>3050b2e</code></a> Merge pull request #&#8203;23 from GinjiBan/master</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rstacruz/jsdom-global/commit/5a283689ecac280e45df4fbe6b992d30ff20e059\"><code>5a28368</code></a> jsdom 10 doesn&#x27;t support node &lt; 6</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rstacruz/jsdom-global/commit/00f0671744e64ca0cb39d7f3ab7d60974f2be0cb\"><code>00f0671</code></a> rm defaultview</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rstacruz/jsdom-global/commit/228cfd9ff80793d200e2d8cebccd1266253dbf25\"><code>228cfd9</code></a> new JSDOM</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rstacruz/jsdom-global/commit/ff5c1e18a9771ea36d0ee824806522ab4dfb5587\"><code>ff5c1e1</code></a> update dep versions</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rstacruz/jsdom-global/commit/d3904226a01253f3312fca9f1230f68b5aca9259\"><code>d390422</code></a> Release v2.1.1</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rstacruz/jsdom-global/commit/42ab527d26ae8de1385bd95cb9e254b707cf2406\"><code>42ab527</code></a> Export XMLHttpRequest</li>\n</ul>\n<p></details></p>\n<hr />\n<p>This PR has been generated by <a href=\"https://renovateapp.com\">Renovate Bot</a>.</p>",
